eru-lam-loan-khan-dai-tai-nga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nissu Cauti t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 fan n\u1eef n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0110T Peru m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i. \u1ede World Cup 2018, Nissu c\u0169ng sang Nga \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&quot;Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u&quot; fan n\u1eef n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng c\u1ee7a Nissu Cauti \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb 3 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Peru chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i Copa America 2015 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Chile. Nissu v\u1edbi bi\u1ec7t danh &quot;em g\u00e1i&quot; Peru lu\u00f4n khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c m\u00e1y quay ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u00f4 khi di\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e1ch \u0111i\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n khoe tr\u1ecdn v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p 3 v\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m, Nissu c\u00f2n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd c\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ebfu Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Peru trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 t\u1ea1i Montevideo. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, Edinson Cavani \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t gi\u00fap Uruguay gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Nissu \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef l\u1eddi h\u1ee9a tr\u00fat b\u1ecf xi\u00eam y khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1nh m\u00e0y r\u00e2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t phen m\u00e3n nh\u00e3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00ecnh y\u00eau c\u00f9ng \u0110T Peru, Nissu \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 36 n\u0103m qua &quot;La Rojiblanca&quot; m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n tham d\u1ef1. R\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc cho Peru v\u00e0 &quot;em g\u00e1i&quot; Nissu, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u00e2m c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u1ee7a Nissu - &quot;Bravo, Peru. Bra off, Nissu&quot; (Peru ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean, qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o Nissu tr\u00fat xu\u1ed1ng), ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t Peru ch\u01a1i kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/nissu2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"317","checkdouble":"188819"},{"date":"14:59 18/06","title":"HLV Tunisia c\u00f4ng khai c\u00e1ch ng\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/hlv-tunisia-cong-khai-cach-ngang-duong-doi-tuyen-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Nabil Maaloul c\u1ee7a Tunisia cho r\u1eb1ng Dele Alli l\u00e0 v\u0169 kh\u00ed nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i, Tunisia c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i phong t\u1ecfa th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Maaloul e ng\u1ea1i Alli</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh v\u00e0 Tunisia s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nhau trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bang-g-world-cup-2018-nguoi-au-bieu-duong-suc-manh-421-187996.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018</span> n\u00e0y. Panama v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harry Kane \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u0103ng hoa \u1edf Tottenham. Nh\u01b0ng HLV Nabil Maaloul c\u1ee7a Tunisia cho r\u1eb1ng Alli m\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn h\u01a1n t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tunisia e ng\u1ea1i Alli c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Tunisia e ng\u1ea1i Alli c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/hlv-tunisia-cong-khai-cach-ngang-duong-tuyen-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Nabil Maaloul e ng\u1ea1i Alli</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cDele Alli l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u. T\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 hay \u0111\u00e1 l\u1ec7ch c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. T\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cV\u1edbi t\u00f4i, Tunisia c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i theo s\u00e1t Alli. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u1ed1i li\u00ean k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1edbi Harry Kane. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng nhau t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u \u1edf Spurs.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cN\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 m\u1ed1i li\u00ean k\u1ebft \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn. Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u00f3 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed3ng nh\u1ea5t cao. H\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u0169 kh\u00ed trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng v\u0169 kh\u00ed nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Dele Alli. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nh\u00e3n quan v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Alli</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 v\u1eeba qua, Alli \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 9 b\u00e0n \u1edf Premier League. T\u00ednh tr\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, sao tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Spurs ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 14 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft FA Cup.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf Spurs, Dele Alli ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Anh vs Tunisia:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-tunisia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-196-thu-da-keu-dot-dung-xit-421-188765.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1862018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-tunisia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-196-thu-da-keu-dot-dung-xit-421-188765.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Tunisia vs Anh (1h00 ng\u00e0y 19/6): Th\u1eed \u0111\u00e3 k\u00eau, \u0111\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eebng x\u1ecbt</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Tunisia vs Anh b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018: Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareth Southgate ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tham chi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh trang l\u00e0 chu\u1ed7i 10 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-tunisia-tham-du-world-cup-2018-an-so-vung-carthage-421-187819.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/dt-tunisia-tham-du-world-cup-2018-an-so-vung-carthage.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-tunisia-tham-du-world-cup-2018-an-so-vung-carthage-421-187819.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Tunisia tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018: \u1ea8n s\u1ed1 v\u00f9ng Carthage</span><br>\r\nT\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh sau 12 n\u0103m v\u1eafng b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t Ch\u00e2u Phi chi\u1ebfu theo th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng FIFA, li\u1ec7u Tunisia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"316","checkdouble":"188820"},{"date":"15:35 18/06","title":"\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft cho chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/15/da-nang-tra-gia-dat-cho-chien-thang-nguoc-dong-truoc-hagl.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T Anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 y\u00eau m\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Tunisia c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 \u201cc\u1ea3 gan\u201d \u0111i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i thi\u00ean m\u1ec7nh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u:</em> Anh vs Tunisia<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian: </em>1h ng\u00e0y 19/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>S\u00e2n Volgograd Arena (th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Volgograd)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Anh 0.91 *0:1*-0.96 Tunisia<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Nhi\u1ec1u -0.94*2 1/4*0.87 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Tunisia v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Bongda24hvn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Tunisia v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Bongda24hvn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-tunisia-va-du-doan-anh-vs-tunisia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Tunisia 1h ng\u00e0y 19/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nAnh kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng g\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/4-van-de-ton-dong-o-dt-anh-truoc-ngay-ra-quan-world-cup-2018-421-187989.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate</span> l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. 10 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1o cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Tam s\u01b0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea7y y\u00ean t\u00e2m tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c Anh ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 t\u1ed1t cho c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n hi\u1ebfm.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Euro 2016, \u0110T Anh d\u01b0\u1edbi tay HLV Roy Hodgson \u0111\u00e3 to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ra sao? H\u1ecd h\u00f2a 2/3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi thua nh\u1ee5c nh\u00e3 Iceland 1-2 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eric Dier hay Jordan Henderson cho DT Anh tai World Cup 2018?\" title=\"Eric Dier hay Jordan Henderson cho \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018?\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/5-cau-hoi-cho-doi-tuyen-Anh-truoc-tran-ra-quan-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2014, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh Hodgson c\u00f9ng Anh b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 4 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n khi giao h\u1eefu. Nh\u01b0ng khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 thua li\u1ec1n 2 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Italia, Urguay \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c v\u1edbi Costa Rica, h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t h\u1ed3n v\u00e0 b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 0-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, tr\u01b0\u1edbc Euro 2012, Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ebft Na Uy t\u1edbi B\u1ec9 khi giao h\u1eefu. R\u1ed3i r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, Tam s\u01b0 c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Hodgson c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111i t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 1/8 (thua Italia sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m). C\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e2m tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Tunisia kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 d\u1ec5 \u0111o\u00e1n. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi song \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. B\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tay Ban Nha 1-0 Tunisia Thiago\" title=\"T\u00e2y Ban Nha 1-0 Tunisia Thiago\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/10/DfRuwodXkAASmET.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tunisia (tr\u00e1i) c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Tony Adams \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i \u00fd: \u0110T Anh ch\u1eb3ng \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Tottenham. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London su\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng \u1edf m\u1ee9c ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi ch\u00fang.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Anh c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 5 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Tottenham v\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Danny Rose c\u00f2n 50/50, nh\u1eefng Kieran Trippier, Dele Alli, Eric Dier, Harry Kane \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f3 thay th\u1ebf. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 Kyle Walker t\u1eebng c\u00f3 8 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Spurs. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0103n \u00fd l\u1edbn song v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u1eb1m \u1edf kh\u00ed ch\u1ea5t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alli DT Anh\" title=\"Alli \u0110T Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/chat-brazil-duy-nhat-trong-doi-tuyen-anh-nam-o-ai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110T&nbsp;Anh d\u1ef1a nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Tottenham</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u00e9t v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9, Tunisia t\u1ef1 tin kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e9m g\u00ec so v\u1edbi Anh. 10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o World Cup 2018, &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng v\u00f9ng Carthage&rdquo; ch\u1ec9 thua \u0111\u00fang 1 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i 5 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nRi\u00eang m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi TBN, Tunisia ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng l\u1edbn ch\u00e2u \u00c2u d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m duy nh\u1ea5t 1 l\u1ea7n tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch ph\u00fat 84. Kh\u00f4ng may, c\u00fa s\u00fat xa c\u1ee7a Iago Aspas ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m l\u1ea1i \u0111i r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Nabil Maaloul th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng h\u00e0nh trang \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Tunisia t\u1ef1 tin b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi World Cup 2018. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, h\u1ecd h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd g\u00e2y ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho Anh gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi kh\u00e1c \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Khan hi\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3 trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh 5 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, \u0110T Anh h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 n\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap cho Tam s\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n thua sau 8 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danny Rose hay Ashley Young cho DT Anh tai World Cup 2018?\" title=\"Danny Rose hay Ashley Young cho \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018?\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/Mourinho-tin-DT-Anh-se-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-tai-Nga-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110T&nbsp;Anh h\u01b0\u1edbng nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i, Anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. 8 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3, d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng Costa Rica, Nigeria, Lithuania r\u1ed3i Slovenia, Tam s\u01b0 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 8 b\u00e0n. Anh ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/doi-truong-harry-kane-noi-gi-truoc-tran-ra-quan-cua-dt-anh-421-188730.html\" target=\"_blank\">ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng Harry Kane</span> v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t khi t\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp, h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u01a1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi, nh\u1eafm m\u1eaft c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft Tunisia s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed5 b\u00ea t\u00f4ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 h\u1ed3n nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt, khoa h\u1ecdc. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i &ldquo;l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba \u0111en&rdquo;, Tunisia ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n sau 6 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n